Package: Z.gtsummary.addons
Type: Package
Title: Functions for modifying gtsummary baseline tables in various ways
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Zheer Kejlberg Al-Mashhadi
Maintainer: Zheer Kejlberg Al-Mashhadi <nomail@me.com>
Description: This package contains functions to modify tbl_summary/tbl_svysummary baseline tables.
    The first function, add_SMD, adds standardised mean differences (SMDs) between any number of groups in a baseline table.
    The second function, round_5_gtsummary, helps avoid microdata in tables by rounding counts to nearest 5 (and adjusting percentages accordingly).
